title: MONDAY 5/17 - ROOKIE MINICAMPS
itunes:title: MONDAY 5/17 - ROOKIE MINICAMPS
description:
Rookie minicamps took place over the weekend, and in Chicago Justin Fields impressing head coach Matt Nagy (0:33) already. Titans rookie Caleb Farley (0:54) ahead of the curve despite being sidelined with an injury...Cowboys head coach Mike McCarthy (2:00) talks about Dak Prescott's return and Packers head coach Matt LaFleur (3:03) gives an update on Aaron Rodgers. Plus, the Giants bring in Kelvin Benjamin (4:17) as a tight end
